  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Game purchase includes chapter 1 and six challenges in challenge mode. Additional chapters and challenges will be released in future DLC.</i><br><br><strong><u>ZARDY'S CAVE</u></strong><br><br>You've fallen down a mysterious hole in the middle of a farm field... But what horrors await you deep underground?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beneath the Surface</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/052d4f1f0e2aee6d05a40c0404a80481.poster.avif?t=1732125606\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/052d4f1f0e2aee6d05a40c0404a80481.webm?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/052d4f1f0e2aee6d05a40c0404a80481.mp4?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strange, giant plants sprouted from underneath the field of corn. Ghastly scarecrows appeared soon after and chased you down a giant hole. When you awoke, you realized you were somewhere strange. But most importantly you were not safe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt to the Underground</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/fe1a77aa096a991d683d92c01efc677c.poster.avif?t=1732125606\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/fe1a77aa096a991d683d92c01efc677c.webm?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/fe1a77aa096a991d683d92c01efc677c.mp4?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The subterranean world under the farm is full of surprises. From scary monsters to peculiar puzzles, you must overcome each obstacle that stands in your way. Climb rocks, cut vines, grow plants, and crawl through the dirt. You will navigate dark mazes and large open spaces while you evade those who hunt you in the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover What Lies Below</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/5f3e66d6899d694a12818cf17b01c8b5.poster.avif?t=1732125606\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/5f3e66d6899d694a12818cf17b01c8b5.webm?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/5f3e66d6899d694a12818cf17b01c8b5.mp4?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You will need to listen, watch, and move carefully through earthy labyrinths as you utilize tools you find on your journey. Delve deeper into the underground and avoid getting caught as you try to uncover the mystery beneath the farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beyond the Cave</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/6334051081826049ec94dfbb2ca3dde7.poster.avif?t=1732125606\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/6334051081826049ec94dfbb2ca3dde7.webm?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/6334051081826049ec94dfbb2ca3dde7.mp4?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your skill from story mode into challenge mode where you'll encounter new scenarios and levels to overcome. From fields, to caves, to places too strange to describe - can you survive and reach the goal?</p>",
