_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/6334051081826049ec94dfbb2ca3dde7.webm?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079980/extras/6334051081826049ec94dfbb2ca3dde7.mp4?t=1732125606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your skill from story mode into challenge mode where you'll encounter new scenarios and levels to overcome. From fields, to caves, to places too strange to describe - can you survive and reach the goal?</p>",
